Hi CD Community!

We developed a free & accessible FRC Chatbot, ARCINATOR, and now, accompanied by the Song and Artwork of the day, it‚Äôs available for use! Wondering what type of battery you must use in your robot, or unsure about how heavy it can be? You can use ARCINATOR to ask any question about the game manual! Simply use the provided link to access ARCINATOR, ask questions in over 150 languages about the game manuals (including past seasons), WPILIB documentation, and The Blue Alliance team data! Especially if you‚Äôre a Rookie team, please consider checking it out to learn more about the game rules and regulations for this seasonüêâ
